OL,3,CNew law banning XL bully dogs in
OL,4,CScotland to come into force from Friday
OL,6,FScotland's ban on XL bully dogs comes
OL,7,Finto effect just days after police
OL,8,Fwere called to an incident involving
OL,9,Fthe breed, as ITV News Correspondent
OL,10,FPeter Smith explains
OL,12,FOwning an XL bully without putting
OL,13,Fsafeguards in place will be illegal in
OL,14,FScotland from Friday.
OL,16,FThe measures, which replicate those
OL,17,Fintroduced by the UK government, will
OL,18,Frequire owners to muzzle their XL
OL,19,Fbully dogs and keep them on a lead
OL,20,Fwhen in public.
