OL,3,CNew law banning XL bully dogs in
OL,4,CScotland to come into force from Friday
OL,6,FAdditionally, it will be illegal to
OL,7,Fsell, abandon, give away or breed the
OL,8,Fdogs, with penalties for any breaches
OL,9,Fof the new safeguards including up to
OL,10,Fsix months imprisonment and a maximum
OL,11,Ffine of #5,000.
OL,13,FA second phase of measures will be
OL,14,Fbrought into law in July by the
OL,15,FScottish government, and will require
OL,16,Fowners to have an exemption
OL,17,Fcertificate.
