OL,3,CNew law banning XL bully dogs in
OL,4,CScotland to come into force from Friday
OL,6,FScottish community safety minister
OL,7,FSiobhian Brown , after the Scottish
OL,8,Fgovernment had initially decided
OL,9,Fagainst following the UK government's
OL,10,Flead.
OL,12,FSuch rules on XL bully dogs came into
OL,13,Fforce in England and Wales at the
OL,14,Fstart of 2024.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News, Ms Brown
OL,17,Fexplained the reasoning for the
OL,18,FScottish government's U-turn, saying
OL,19,Fit had been "put into a corner".
