OL,3,CNew law banning XL bully dogs in
OL,4,CScotland to come into force from Friday
OL,6,FShe said: "We've been put into a
OL,7,Fcorner where they've (XL bully's) been
OL,8,Fbanned from the UK government and it's
OL,9,Fled to a loophole."
OL,11,FPressed on whether she believes XL
OL,12,Fbully's to be dangerous, Ms Brown said
OL,13,Fshe does not think "breeds as such can
OL,14,Fbe dangerous, but I do think you have
OL,15,Fto have responsible ownership".
OL,17,FIn recent weeks, police have responded
OL,18,Fto two separate dog attack incidents
OL,19,Fin Scotland, which both ended with an
OL,20,FXL bully-type dog being destroyed.
