OL,4,CScotland to come into force from Friday
OL,6,FWhen asked if the Scottish government
OL,7,Fregrets the attacks that have taken
OL,8,Fplace, Ms Brown refused to answer,
OL,9,Finstead saying: "We do not know if
OL,10,Fthose dog attacks were XL bully's or
OL,11,Fnot."
OL,13,FShe added: "All I want to get across
OL,14,Ftoday is we are copying the
OL,15,Flegislation that has been rushed
OL,16,Fthrough from England and Wales."
