OL,6,FScottish ministers have confirmed they
OL,7,Fwill use the same XL bully definition
OL,8,Fas the UK government, which states the
OL,9,Flarge dogs have "a muscular body and
OL,10,Fblocky head, suggesting great strength
OL,11,Fand power for its size".
OL,13,FThe estimated height of the dogs is
OL,14,Fapproximately 51cm at the withers for
OL,15,Fan adult male and 48cm for an adult
OL,16,Ffemale.
